36:04.829 --> 36:06.997
and then he gets stuck

36:07.081 --> 36:09.666
<i>and he starts
screaming for David to help,</i>

36:09.750 --> 36:11.409
and David's
trying to pull him up.

36:11.493 --> 36:13.244
<i>It's not working.</i>

36:13.329 --> 36:16.256
- Inmate Sweat would throw
a bedsheet back to him

36:16.415 --> 36:20.251
<i>and utilize the bed sheet to
help pull him through the pipe</i>

36:20.344 --> 36:23.180
because it was a pretty tight
fit for inmate Matt

36:23.264 --> 36:28.843
<i>- After a long struggle,
Matt finally makes it through.</i>

36:28.928 --> 36:34.024
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:34.108 --> 36:36.267
<i>- David popped his head
out of the manhole,</i>

36:36.352 --> 36:40.030
<i>looked around,
